data.description: Escape to the tranquility of one-story living in the heart of Bell Township, Jefferson County, PA, where we've discovered a true gem at 641 Albion Road, Punxsutawney. This charming home eliminates the hassle of a basement while still offering the convenience of a 2-car attached garage. Well water and an on-site septic system. The floor plan seamlessly accommodates your lifestyle with 3 bedrooms and 1 bath, providing a cozy retreat for you and your family. Step into the heart of the home, where the kitchen has Hickory cabinets, a farmhouse-style sink, and a center island highlighted with granite. The metal roof ensures durability, and the sprawling yard is adorned with a variety of shade trees, creating a picturesque setting, with Fencing for your family pet. This residence is  a dream fulfilled in a dream location. Numerous updates, making this home feel like a haven where modern comforts meet the charm of rural living.
